{"tid":1563051,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"五大訴求能否達成，只在於一線之差","createTime":"2019-09-12T09:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T13:45:54.000Z","uid":128239,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8621ae18a08d05b47adc14f95e7b2de5d4e505a8","tid":1563051,"uid":128239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:12:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">Tldr嘅直接拉落去睇二樓<br />\n</span></span></strong></span><br />\n首先請大家認清現實，<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人抗爭可以頂到今時今日，背後原因只有一個：美國。</span></strong>如果今次單純係香港人vs中共的話，其他國家只作有限度介入的話，呢場運動一早收左皮，香港人一係被血腥鎮壓，一係就變維吾爾人。所以，請大家持續保持警覺，唔好浸淫喺盲目樂觀之下。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>背景</ins></span></span></strong></strong><br />\n另一個unwanted truth就係美國國內係有唔少奶共派，之前接待葉劉個Steve Daines就係一例，仲未計AOC, Ilhan Omar 呢堆冇腦左膠，香港人權及民主法案要喺國會拎多過2/3支持，其實唔係十拿九穩。更可怕嘅野喺後頭，大家都聽過參議院只要一個參議員Hold 起條法案就可以無限期延遲審議，直至個參議員唔再hold起佢為止。遺憾地，奶共嘅Steve Daines 正正就係一位參議員，佢會唔會受共匪收買，癲到押上自己政治生涯去奶共，呢個仲係未知之數。<br />\n<br />\n好啦，比你過到參眾兩院，之後仲有總統嗰關要過，冇錯，侵侵出晒名反中，但同時佢都出晒名係利益主義者，假設共匪讓步讓到應承美國所有貿易要求，答應唔再想獨霸香港，而美國又有信心keep到佢喺香港嘅stake嘅話，佢仲會唔會咁care香港嘅人權同民主狀況？到時佢隨時一個veto就收左條人權民主法案皮。<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">喺度要講番即使參眾兩院以2/3高票通過法案，總統依然有權veto否決議案，呢個時候議案就會發回參眾兩院重審，2/3呢條界線嘅用處係如果參眾兩院再有2/3議員支持法案，咁即使總統反對，呢條法案都會生效。</span></strong>可惜，<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>歷史上只有7%咁嘅例子</strong></span>，大多數法案喺總統否決後再審就會喺參眾兩院收皮，香港人權及民主法案會唔會成為呢7%？機會唔係冇，但極難，始終香港嘅問題對美國而言唔係切膚之痛，除非有人有心借題發揮搞鳩侵侵而又成功，否則萬一真係veto左嘅話香港人權及民主法案就好大機會收皮。"},{"pid":"eef0d98b27b05332dd4656ae7ab8a77f3a5bbfde","tid":1563051,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:12:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"614c1679e554c2ba2a196a8ca5a2792c8965c584","tid":1563051,"uid":128239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:15:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>要點奶美國？</ins></span></span></strong><br />\n好啦，背景講完。咁我地依家有咩可以做？勇武嘅請繼續勇武，但文宣、和理非都要更多地target美國。文宣方面多d出英文文宣，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>日前見到Facebook 作者個page想寫報告去美國制裁奶共派（<strong>link:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/972393926144079/posts/2639802356069886?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F972393926144079%2Fposts%2F2639802356069886%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIb%2F5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=86bd73f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/972393926144079/posts/2639802356069886?sfns=mo</a></strong><br />\n），呢個係可取之計</strong></span>，同時可以整個網站，記錄低眾賣港賊嘅罪行，呢d報告亦可以比其他國家做參考。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">另外以後每次示威都要舉美國旗唱美國國歌</span></strong>，美國patriot 嘅力量不容小覷，好多美國人佩服香港人對美國嘅敬重同追求民主自由嘅決心。舉美國旗仲可以施加壓力比美國，諗下連香港呢個國際金融中心，兼且美國有晒stake嘅地方舉晒美國旗求救，美國都wfc的話，以後仲有冇其他國家信美國喺關鍵時候會保佢？所以，為面子，亦都為保持喺世界嘅影響力，美國需要出面保住香港。<br />\n<br />\n最後，所有香港人都要認清現實，無論有幾反美都好，依家美國係唯一一個有能力同有決心協助香港對抗中共嘅國家，要贏中共，除左背靠美國外別無他法。<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">所有反美嘅舉動（e.g. 搶美國旗）必須制止，而香港人亦應該keep住上twitter，reddit向美國人陳情，英文好嘅可以嘗試投稿去美國媒體</span></strong>，擴大美國人對香港嘅關注同支持。切記，成功同失敗只有一線之差，萬一美國唔支持香港，香港下場只會比悲慘更悲慘。"},{"pid":"143089a388e093c24f7e7fe2ebb5453a31b663e2","tid":1563051,"uid":128239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:17:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"371f72321cbdb3fd4f3d74b23ad6b57f45000550","tid":1563051,"uid":128239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:17:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61029f6a8aa44533702ed4e40e31b1722cdce048","tid":1563051,"uid":128239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:19:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"efe834b8a722570ac840acfdad0aa918e23ada79","tid":1563051,"uid":128239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:20:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"17dfe6f6b42c545fe903977e094e0d9cdfe53f9e","tid":1563051,"uid":128239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:21:28.000Z","msg":"長文冇人睇？"},{"pid":"94dde501e6c4473f98b928c524338d25577be38b","tid":1563051,"uid":128239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:23:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a8f9619a9697a0100c527c8b1401c858d8d5900","tid":1563051,"uid":128239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38d23992155a4e9b2a9157c2518c8e1b242075a","tid":1563051,"uid":128239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:25:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"540cf2f11b508bd2e600dc7de80317b5ea01ef18","tid":1563051,"uid":128239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T09:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375f8d29f9bb7cf7d3a38053b135a5f705ea82f7","tid":1563051,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:02:57.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3a26ca98a0fda05eb9dfbf4645c9d5284c9a23","tid":1563051,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:04:02.000Z","msg":"今晚7點  IFC  <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美國國歌</span></span>  曬支那冷!!!"},{"pid":"07fbecf3022270984a51085d4bc7adab5bd05a34","tid":1563051,"uid":253952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:07:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/oh.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a9eab677d6764524129db7267928d5b41885dd","tid":1563051,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:12:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9629d72eb96688c422e43eb3326fdc35421ee8d","tid":1563051,"uid":128239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:25:11.000Z","msg":"再自推"},{"pid":"ed14575fce75791c7c44685722a04960077f33b1","tid":1563051,"uid":128239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:45:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}